WordClash is a word matching game for all age.
In this game we tried add as many Swing component as possible.

How to set PC for game

Database Side
1. Install phpmyadmin
2. Create a Database named : wordclash_db
3. Create table(column) : user(user_name, score), word_easy(word), word_medium(word),word_hard(word), word_tb(word)
4. Import data from csv files located in project structure --> resource/kidsWords
5. Import csv files according to their naming convension to the repected table

IDE Side
1. Clone the project to local pc
2. Import the project in IDE
3. Add mysql library from project structure for database connection.
4. Run the Main file
5. Enjoy
